### Create club
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/clubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "FC Stockholm",
  "slug": "fc-stockholm"
}

### Create club - duplicate slug
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/clubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "FC Stockholm 2",
  "slug": "fc-stockholm"
}

### Create club - invalid slug format
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/clubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "FC Stockholm",
  "slug": "FC Stockholm!"
}